# WhatsApp (Phase 4 only)

Do not implement until Phase 4 unless user explicitly requests early spike.

## Location

- All Baileys code under `main/whatsapp/`
- Orchestration in `whatsapp.service.ts` — renderer uses IPC only

## Anti-ban

- All outbound messages pass through rate-limited queue
- Enforce limits from `anti_ban_config` — see `docs/WHATSAPP.md`
- Bulk/reminders require Admin approval queue
- Log every send to `whatsapp_logs`

## Provider pattern

- Interface `WhatsAppProvider` — implement `BaileysProvider` first for future API swap

## Inbox

- One conversation per customer phone
- Assignment lock prevents two staff replying simultaneously
- Sort rules documented in `docs/WHATSAPP.md`
